      "detail": "No technical mechanism traces output value to specific data contributions with the precision needed for fair allocation between parties. The audit cannot allocate output value to individual data sources because it cannot trace the derivation chain from training input to commercial output. Unallocated output value is the direct commercial consequence of the verification gap that this pattern creates and sustains."
    },
    "Derived Value Capture": {
      "value": "Processor captures",
      "memo": "The processor captures all derived value while the declared-only audit cannot verify whether the underlying derivation actually complied with applicable licence terms.",
      "detail": "Derived products, applications, fine-tuned models, and downstream commercial ecosystems generate substantial ongoing value for the processor. The compliance audit cannot verify that the derivation process followed licence terms because no derivation tracking infrastructure exists at production scale. Processor capture of derived value proceeds unchecked because genuine verification of derivation compliance is absent from the audit framework. The derived value flows entirely to the processor regardless of whether actual processing matched the declared compliance posture."
    },
    "Risk Allocation / Backstop": {
      "value": "Disclaimed",
      "memo": "Risk is disclaimed through terms referencing the audit as governance evidence, transferring liability based on a compliance verification that did not actually verify.",
      "detail": "Terms of service and commercial contracts reference the compliance audit as evidence of responsible data handling and governance practices. This documentation shifts liability to downstream users and data contributors who relied on the audit's published conclusions in good faith. Risk is disclaimed by pointing to a verification process that did not actually verify compliance at the technical level where it matters. The disclaimer rests on and derives its apparent legitimacy from the appearance of adequate verification."
    },
    "Capital": {
      "value": "Operating",
