      "detail": "The processor operates in a jurisdiction with strong legal institutions, independent courts, and reliable commercial enforcement mechanisms for contract disputes. Courts in allied jurisdictions could order deeper verification but currently lack the technical expertise, tools, and trained personnel to conduct it. Allied jurisdiction provides robust legal process and institutional credibility for enforcement but no technical audit infrastructure for AI compliance. The gap between legal enforcement authority and technical audit capability sustains the pattern even in the strongest legal systems."
    },
    "Vertical Integration": {
      "value": "Application-only",
      "memo": "Application-only integration means the audit focuses narrowly on the application layer without examining the underlying model composition or infrastructure-level compliance.",
