      "detail": "Competing labs and AI companies face the same compliance verification challenges and the same market pressure to ship quickly without delay. None has a commercial incentive to invest in deeper audit unilaterally because the cost falls on one party while competitors benefit from cheaper compliance. The competitive dynamic creates a race to the bottom in verification rigour where minimum viable compliance becomes the industry standard."
    },
    "Race Pressure": {
